* **"Content"** means all images, videos, benchmark tables, PDFs, and other data files contained in this repository **excluding** any source code or binary executable files.
* **"Evaluation Purpose"** means internal, non‑commercial testing, academic research, or technical feasibility assessment of Druma One technology.

